OL,3,CHead of Caldey Abbey apologises for
OL,4,C'great suffering' of abused children
OL,6,FIn the wake of the report, Father
OL,7,FRossey said: "It is with deep sorrow
OL,8,Fand regret that I have read in the
OL,9,Freview of the great suffering of
OL,10,Fchildren who were abused by Father
OL,11,FThaddeus Kotik and the closed culture
OL,12,Fof secrecy and cover-up which kept
OL,13,Fthis hidden.
OL,15,F"It is clear opportunities were missed
OL,16,Fto stop the abuse of children. It is
OL,17,Fparticularly heartbreaking to hear
OL,18,Fchildren spoke up to adults and no
OL,19,Faction was taken."
